data.title: Michigan's Largest Indoor Outlet Mall and Entertainment Center
data.meta_description: Great Lakes Crossing Outlets has over 25 stores and restaurants that can't be found anywhere else in Michigan, including SEA LIFE Michigan Aquarium, LEGOLAND Discovery Center, Rainforest Cafe, Saks Fifth Avenue Off 5th, Neiman Marcus Last Call Clearance Center, Calvin Klein Company Store, Coach Factory, Michael Kors Oulet and Polo Ralph Lauren Factory Store.
